content.body:
### Shop 9.50x15 Tire Size 
The 9.50x15 tire size is one you’ll find on the front of tractors, as well as wagons, seeders, and other towed agricultural equipment that sees occasional highway use. These types of ag tires need to be durable, with reinforced casings that resist damage from stubble and other debris, as well as offering good flotation, traction, and handling. 

Looking for a new 9.50x15 tire for the front of your tractor? Check out the [Carlisle Farm Specialist F-1 Hwy Service Implement](https://simpletire.com/brands/carlisle-tires/farm-specialist-f-1-hwy-service-implement), Titan Hi-Flotation I-1, Crop Max F2, and Harvest King Front Farm 4R, as each tire offers excellent traction, durability, and flotation.

Whether you drive a tractor, wagon, seeder, or something else, SimpleTire has a 9.50x15 tire that meets your needs at a great price!
